{"tid":2122223,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國將一如中國的同等地位對待香港, 咁係咪要驅逐香港駐海外經貿辦先?","createTime":"2020-07-24T01:13:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T11:17:40.000Z","uid":14918,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"58f553d0d0aebd0b28dba2f2257f644c7f779bc9","tid":2122223,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T01:13:16.000Z","msg":"加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n華盛頓辦事處<br />\n紐約辦事處<br />\n三藩市辦事處<br />\n<br />\n仲要收回佢地D特權及豁免權<br />\n<br />\n至於日後正苦可以考慮開設駐德黑蘭經貿辦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aa068bbe4df3cca7e17aca9994c6009377706cc","tid":2122223,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T01:18:17.000Z","msg":"前，十一個香港駐海外經貿辦（即駐倫敦、布魯塞爾、日內瓦、華盛頓、紐約、三藩市、東京、多倫多、新加坡、悉尼和柏林等地的經貿辦）已獲相關當地政府授予若干特權及豁免權，以便利各經貿辦在不受干預的情況下履行職務。概括而言，<span class=\"red\">經貿辦可享有的特權及豁免權主要包括處所、來往公文和公務檔案及文件不得侵犯，以及處所和代表人員免稅。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b4591388d7d63574a21ed9e1727705fa43e8d53","tid":2122223,"uid":124439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T01:29:56.000Z","msg":"再一次顯示特區班膠官點樣累死香港"},{"pid":"22c1cb9436116ed8396034ef69857380c6f5eca6","tid":2122223,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b4591388d7d63574a21ed9e1727705fa43e8d53","tid":2122223,"uid":124439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T01:29:56.000Z","msg":"再一次顯示特區班膠官點樣累死香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T01:39:46.000Z","msg":"仲有中共既<br />\n尊重一國呀嘛, 咁香港用番大陸D領事服務咪算"},{"pid":"7e15ff4d80f7174f7422fd5771a40d65a5b9f512","tid":2122223,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:21:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e667d7274b75531c5c587c1bb259a7c5e0884f4a","tid":2122223,"uid":83819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":